description:
Here are two equally experienced novice wrestlers.
Both really want a win, but only one will get it. Both
have paid their dues, and now one will walk off the
mat with a victory. Kat hates losing and doesn't ever let
up, no matter how many points she might have fallen
behind. Darling has been training in the tradition of
high [REDACTED] wrestling style on her own time. It's
all about the training.
title: The Grappler (0-2)
